reviewText: I purchased this expecting it in its entirety....only saw 5-10mins...rest of DVD was blank. I would like a refund or another DVD...paid too much to just throw my money away....
Very very disappointed. This was 10 minutes in length!! Total ripoff. Take my advice and don't buy this bootlegged crap.

As a frequent customer of Amazon, I am highly disappointed  at the actual length of the video. I was not excepting  the video to be 5-10 mins in length. I feel like I was duked. Next time, I would really appreciate it if Amazon posted the actual length of the video.
